com.bitctrl.util

Class TwoDimensionalMap<R,C,D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bitctrl.util.TwoDimensionalMap<R,C,D>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - the key type for the rows
    C - the key type for the columns
    D - the value type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITwoDimensionalMap<R,C,D>, Serializable

    public class TwoDimensionalMap<R,C,D>
extends Object
implements Serializable, ITwoDimensionalMap<R,C,D>
    Provides a two-dimensional map. The data entry matrix are automatically filled up so that every row respective every column has the same size.
    Author:
    BitCtrl Systems GmbH, schnepel
